Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.56,0:00:26.50,NarTop,,0,0,0,,Utajima is an island less than 2.5 miles around, with a population of 1,400. {lit: circumference of less than one li - less than one third of a mile - not sure how it became "2.5 miles" in translation; in the book translation I have it's "and a coastline of something under three miles."}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.55,NarTop,,0,0,0,,Octopi comprise 80%\N of the island's fishing haul.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's old man\N Miyata Teru's new ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... Must be around 150 tons.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.83,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, gotta be more'n 180.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, he sure thinks he's hot shit \Nsince he went an' got rich.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.69,0:01:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys know old man Teru \Nis bringing his daughter back here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.39,0:01:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Story is, after old man Teru \Nlost his son last year,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.49,0:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he got lonely,\N so he took his daughter Hatsue,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.61,0:01:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd been adopted into another family,\N and made her come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.46,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like that stubborn\N old guy, all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.16,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he wants to adopt a son-in-law as his heir,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.33,0:01:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,an' I heard she's grown up \Ninto a real looker.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.73,0:01:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All the guys wanna be the heir,\N so they're making a big deal over it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.69,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shinji's father was a skilled fisherman.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was killed by American\N machine-gun fire in Ise Bay
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.65,0:02:01.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,at the end of World War II.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shinji began work right after graduating junior high
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.76,0:02:09.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and dreams of someday having the same kind\N of boat that his father sailed on.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He believes that since he's only 18,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.28,0:02:14.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he's too young to be thinking of girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.63,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough helping here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and fetch the water!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a lotta chunks in it, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be enough for your brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.73,0:03:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.49,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a nuisance that the town generator's still not fixed.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how much money can I have for the school trip?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.24,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as the school rules say.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.02,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but both Isamu and Toru \Nsaid they'd bring more.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason you can go\N on a school trip
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is thanks to all the money \Nyour brother earned and saved for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shinji was in junior high,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.59,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he couldn't have gone on a trip\N even if he wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.66,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you have enough money for you\N to get in trouble with the teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's godsend! Thanks, bro!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.77,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hold it...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lucky, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.14,Overlap,,0,0,0,,That's great!{yokkata}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.20,0:04:18.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next day, fishing was canceled\N due to stormy seas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The firewood on the first floor of the old observation tower on the right is ours. {nc what's that kantekisho but the book tl has it "Shinji's mother had asked a favor of him. The women of the village gathered firewood on the mountain andleft it stored at the top in what had formerly been a military observation tower."}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.36,0:04:42.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,Please, Almighty God, let the sea be calm and the fish be plentiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Let the village continue to thrive,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,and protect and guard my sweet mother and my little brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.98,0:04:53.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,And also, if you could, maybe this is a stupid thing to ask for, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.36,0:05:01.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,Someday, I hope I'll be blessed with a wife \Nwho's beautiful and sweet,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.00,0:05:05.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,for example, like Miyata Terukichi's daughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.88,0:05:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if God's going to punish me \Nfor making such a selfish prayer.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh... I...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lost on my way to the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The lighthouse, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I already noticed it myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this building, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the ruins of an old watchtower.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A watchtower?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. During the war,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an artillery position nearby.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They used it to check the aim of the guns\N during target practice. {originally was "They used to gauge the flight path of the Tomahawks." and I really have to wonder who put that in here, because not only that has nothing to do with the actual line, tomahawk missiles were only around since 1983; book: In former days soldiers had stood on the second-floor balcony, binoculars to their eyes, and checked the aim of\Nthe guns that were fired for target practice from Mt. Konaka on the far side of Irako Cape. Officers had called out from inside the tower to know where the shells were hitting, and the soldiers had called back the ranges.}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But they never got a chance \Nto fire at an American warship.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.64,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to go now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... Your chest...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty tan, but so are you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to the lighthouse?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The lighthouse keeper's wife
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to teach me cooking and flower arrangement.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? She helped me a lot too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.80,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since junior high, I'd been working at sea instead of going to school,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and l hadn't attended enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So you couldn't graduate, \Nthen, could you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.21,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. So the keeper's wife convinced\N the principal that if I couldn't graduate,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.28,0:09:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,my mom, my brother, and I wouldn't be able to make a living.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So they finally gave me my diploma.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice of them! I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a straight shot from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better leave now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Folks like to talk a lot around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, tell me your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shinji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubo Shinji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this meeting\N a secret between us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you. And thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's break for lunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I will after I've done \Na little more work.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.41,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's really bustin' his butt today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because it's payday?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, did ya hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamoto Yasuo's gonna marry Hatsue. {irimuko = man who takes his wife's family name and marries into her family; man who is adopted by his wife's family}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know when Yasuo
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.01,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,left the youth meeting \Nearly the other night?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.69,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was 'cause Miyata Teru invited him\N to Hatsue's homecoming party.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo, you lucky dog.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You get all the girls, man.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.21,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, old man Teru really\N took a liking to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept giving me drinks till I got plastered.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you guys are late.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We were about to close the safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The winch isn't working. \NGive us a hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner will be ready in a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want any.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.36,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Would you rather go\N to the bathhouse with Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to take a bath, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Shinji?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,About the school trip...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.61,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You want your allowance, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he lost his pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'm gonna get my allowance.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is Shinji at home?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he just now got home from work,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and he went right back out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.10,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this at the beach.\N Shinji's name was on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's so kind of you! Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for your pay,\N I gave it to your mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you so mad about a while ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.30,0:14:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were gonna marry\N Yasuo Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! What a pile of crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! I nearly died there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed so hard I could hardly breathe.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, feel the way my heart is beating.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that way I feel much more at peace.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.55,0:16:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going to the lighthouse\N after I get back from fishing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there around that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you balance the whole thing together, you see?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.03,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for your dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.78,0:16:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're always so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, Shinji's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.25,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so kind to us. \NWhy don't you come in?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.75,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, we got a letter from Chiyoko in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked us specifically\N how you were doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet she likes you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come in? \NI'll make hot chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I gotta go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other time...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.28,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Shinji's so very shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's because a beautiful stranger was here today.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you so mad about?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.78,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing to do\N with their daughter!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I swear to God!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,True. They must've fixed the generator!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I see you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere secluded. \NHow about the watchtower?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about next time \NI get a day off from fishing?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.56,0:19:09.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The day Hiroshi and his classmates were leaving for their school trip,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the seas unfortunately grew rough.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Break from exams? Must be tough, \Nbeing an English major.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see you on the ferry\N too often, Chiyoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Has anything new happened on the island?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.58,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Uncle Miyata Teru's brought his daughter back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.58,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name's Hatsue,\N and she's a real beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't open your eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you backing away?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.37,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.31,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do anything to help you \Nnot feel embarrassed?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You take off your clothes too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you should be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not completely naked yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.46,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take it all off, I will too!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.43,0:22:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.77,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump over the fire to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And... And we...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:37.62,Song,,0,0,0,,I write a letter to my loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:44.55,Song,,0,0,0,,I write and tear it, tear it, and write again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:51.09,Song,,0,0,0,,I throw the rolled up paper at the window
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:58.27,Song,,0,0,0,,It's raining outside, just like the tears on my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:06.15,Song,,0,0,0,,Life is a sea, youth is a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:13.24,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, please come and save me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:15.55,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.73,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:26.94,Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:36.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Not a single star in sight, in the sea of ​​sadness
